OL,3,C11 more people to face court charged
OL,4,Cwith Ely riots
OL,6,FMore people have been charged with
OL,7,Frioting in Ely, Cardiff, in May 2023,
OL,8,Fbringing the total to 42.
OL,10,FThere was widespread disruption in the
OL,11,Farea on May 22 as crowds clashed with
OL,12,Fpolice in the immediate aftermath of
OL,13,Ftwo teenagers in the area.
OL,15,FKyrees Sullivan, 16, and Harvey Evans,
OL,16,F15, died after their E-bike crashed,
OL,17,Fminutes after CCTV captured them being
OL,18,Ffollowed by a South Wales Police van.
