OL,3,C11 more people to face court charged
OL,4,Cwith Ely riots
OL,6,FTensions between local people and
OL,7,Fpolice at the scene led to a riot
OL,8,Flasting several hours, during which
OL,9,Ftime dozens of officers were injured,
OL,10,Fproperty was damaged and cars were set
OL,11,Falight.
OL,13,F31 people already appeared before
OL,14,Fcourts in Cardiff charged linked to
OL,15,Fthe riots last year, of these, 27 were
OL,16,Fcharged with riot and four were
OL,17,Faccused of causing or threatening to
OL,18,Fcause criminal damage.
