OL,3,C11 more people to face court charged
OL,4,Cwith Ely riots
OL,6,FNow the Crown prosecution Service has
OL,7,Fconfirmed a further 11 people - ten
OL,8,Fadults and one youth - have also been
OL,9,Fcharged with riot.
OL,11,FThe defendants range between 17 and 43-
OL,12,Fyears-old and will appear before
OL,13,FCardiff Magistrates' and Youth Court
OL,14,Fon January 22 2025.
OL,16,FJenny Hopkins, Chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,17,Ffor CPS Cymru-Wales, said: "The Crown
OL,18,FProsecution Service has authorised
OL,19,FSouth Wales Police to charge a further
OL,20,F11 defendants with the offence of riot.
